<plot>A young recruit to the Carabinieri (the national police force of Italy) is assigned to a remote village in the mountains of Sardinia and participates in the investigation of a murder. His life becomes intertwined with that of the villagers, and his identity is transformed and enriched when he confronts the challenge of pursuing justice in a community that is completely different from his own.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?308129</url></doc>
